Kenya Revenue Authority (KRA) says its relationship with taxpayers has improved after social media engagement on its Customer Relationship Management Solution (CRMS) more than doubled. The taxman said in a statement social media engagement rate has more than doubled from 300 to over 700 engagements per day. ALSO READ:

KRA burns illegal goods worth Sh13m KRA said customer query response time also improved to an average of 15 minutes across all platforms, up from the previous one-hour average turnaround time.